    FAQs

    What days are you open?

     

    The World Food Trucks park is open everyday! All of our food trucks are able to set their individual hours of operation so it is always recommended to contact your favorite food truck directly. 

     

    How can I see a menu?

     

    The best way to see menu information is to contact your favorite food truck directly. Many of our food trucks have menus and information listed online. You can find all of your favorite food trucks and their contact information above. 

    Do you allow pets?

     

    Pets are not allowed in the areas where food is served. service animals are always welcome.

    I own a food truck, how can I become a World Food Trucks vendor?"

     

    Please visit www.worldfoodtrucks.com/joinourteam and fill out your information. If a space opens for your food truck, we will contact you.

    About World Food Trucks

    The first permanent food truck park in Central Florida! Offers fantastic food from around the world. This family-friendly spot also features free, ample parking, clean restrooms and onsite security. Come on out for a delicious bite to eat while enjoying your favorite music all day long or dance under gorgeous Central Florida skies.  Eat, party, dance and meet new like-minded friends at World Food Trucks in Kissimmee. See you there!

    Monday - Thursday 11am - 12am

    Friday - Saturday 11am - 2am

    Sunday 11am - 12am
